WEBVTT

00:00.810 --> 00:04.390
The question we need
answered, Julie, is...

00:04.430 --> 00:07.060
if it were a matter of life and death,

00:07.070 --> 00:10.940
could you kill another human
being to protect your family?

00:12.680 --> 00:15.290
Think carefully before you answer, Julie.

00:18.560 --> 00:24.830
Of course I could. My family?
Of course. How could I not?

00:24.840 --> 00:27.630
Let's see what the polygraph has to say.

00:29.840 --> 00:33.270
You know what that sound
means. Let's hear it again.

00:34.410 --> 00:37.980
That is the sound of a lie.

00:40.200 --> 00:42.330
I...I don't know what
to tell you, Julie,

00:42.340 --> 00:46.070
but,uh,it would appear that
the truth has not been told.

00:46.110 --> 00:48.080
But don't feel bad.

00:48.130 --> 00:51.260
I've been married to some people
I'm not so sure I would kill for.

00:52.020 --> 00:57.410
We'll be right back with Julie, and
more Truth Be Told right after this.

01:02.280 --> 01:04.349
He had that all planned.

01:04.379 --> 01:08.120
He had all of those jokes on
one of those,uh-- on a thing,a...

01:08.130 --> 01:10.130
- Teleprompter.
- On a teleprompter.

01:10.140 --> 01:12.280
- Sure.
- This is so cool.

01:12.290 --> 01:16.060
Yeah,very cool-- if you're going to make
a fool of yourself on national television,

01:16.080 --> 01:17.320
that's the show to do it on.

01:17.360 --> 01:19.720
I think we're going
to need some more wine.

