01:35.660 --> 01:37.770
Oh,good, you're back.
It's about to start again.

01:37.780 --> 01:40.540
I know you're going to
think it's the wine, but...

01:40.550 --> 01:43.680
I could swear I heard something outside.

01:45.740 --> 01:47.470
Maybe you shouldn't go out there.

01:47.490 --> 01:49.080
Maybe it was all in my head.

01:49.110 --> 01:51.920
We're just going to take a look
around, alright? We'll be right back.

01:56.350 --> 01:58.720
Now,where exactly did
you hear the sound?

01:58.740 --> 02:02.640
I was standing in here. I
didn't even put the lights on.

02:03.050 --> 02:07.420
I grabbed some wine at... here.

02:08.889 --> 02:11.190
Listen.

02:12.090 --> 02:14.490
I don't hear anything outside.

02:14.800 --> 02:17.840
It-It's more like it's coming from...

02:22.570 --> 02:25.930
What is going on? What are you watching?

02:26.880 --> 02:30.160
The news just got boring and
you were asleep and I found this.

02:30.200 --> 02:32.910
Oh,this was so scary in college.

02:33.660 --> 02:36.000
Could you shut it off
and we can go to bed?

02:36.030 --> 02:39.690
Your bad movie is making
its way into my bad dreams.

